    <item>
      <title>由于外部缓冲薄弱，惠誉将孟加拉国进一步评级为垃圾级</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/fitch-cuts-bangladesh-deeper-into-junk-on-weak-external-buffers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[惠誉评级周一下调了孟加拉国的主权评级，理由是该国的外部缓冲持续减弱，这可能使这个南亚国家更容易受到冲击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/fitch-cuts-bangladesh-deeper-into-junk-on-weak-external-buffers</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:28:53 GMT</pubDate>
