    <item>
      <title>南澳选举：旅游最小值。关于拉马福萨的未来内阁</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-27/sa-elections-tourism-min-on-ramaphosa-s-future-cabinet-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[现任南非旅游部长兼好党领袖帕特里夏·德里尔 (Patricia de Lille) 告诉彭博社，她不期望继续留任，也不会干涉拉马福萨总统的计划。在南非大选之前，她在开普敦接受了彭博社的詹妮弗·扎巴萨贾 (Jennifer Zabasajja) 的采访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-27/sa-elections-tourism-min-on-ramaphosa-s-future-cabinet-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:18:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>据说 Vedanta 最快将于 6 月考虑出售 10 亿美元的股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/vedanta-is-said-to-weigh-1-billion-share-sale-as-soon-as-june</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，印度大宗商品大亨阿尼尔·阿加瓦尔 (Anil Agarwal) 旗下的韦丹塔有限公司 (Vedanta Ltd.) 正在考虑最快在未来几周内出售股票，这可能筹集高达 850 亿卢比（10 亿美元）的资金。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/vedanta-is-said-to-weigh-1-billion-share-sale-as-soon-as-june</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 May 2024 11:01:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
