      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-27/shanghai-cuts-home-downpayment-as-easing-spreads-to-big-cities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着中国大城市跟进中央政府对房地产行业的援助，金融中心上海降低了首付比例和最低抵押贷款门槛。]]></description>
